SELECT  valor = CASE WHEN valor='ARTICULO' THEN (select isnull(persoart, 'ARTICULO') from config) 
			 WHEN valor='GASTO' THEN (select isnull(persogast, 'GASTO') from config) 
			 WHEN valor='HONORARIO'	then  (select isnull(persohono, 'HONORARIO') from config) 
			 WHEN valor='SUPLIDO' then (select isnull(persoprov, 'SUPLIDO') from config)
			 WHEN valor='VARIOS' then (select isnull(persovari, 'VARIOS') from config)
			 ELSE UPPER(valor) END
FROM [[instancia]advabocom].dbo.gestorvalores
WHERE tabla in ('cuentas')
AND llave = 'tipo'
UNION
select isnull(nullif(valor, ''), REPLACE(etiqueta, 'CuePrevi', 'Previas ')) as valor from [[instancia]advabocom].dbo.etiquetasini where seccion like 'FormExpCue' 
	and 
	(
		(etiqueta = 'CuePrevi' and exists (select bverprevias from config WHERE bverprevias = 1))

	)

SELECT DISTINCT icodcli 
	FROM segcli S
	LEFT JOIN estadosCita EC ON EC.id = S.idEstadoCita
	LEFT JOIN actuaci Act on S.icodigoactupredef = Act.codigo 
	WHERE 
		S.sactuacion LIKE '%{S.sactuacion}%'  
	AND
		S.subusu = {S.subusu} 
	AND 
		S.dfechaact BETWEEN '{S.dfechaact}' AND '{S.dfechaact}'
	AND
		S.fecharealizacion BETWEEN '{S.fecharealizacion}' AND '{S.fecharealizacion}'
	AND
		S.tipo IN ('{S.tipo}')
	AND
		ISNULL(S.acturealizada,0) = {ISNULL(S.acturealizada,0)}
	AND
		Act.referencia LIKE '%{Act.referencia}%'
	AND
		EC.descripcion IN ('{EC.descripcion}') OR (EC.descripcion is NULL AND 'Sin Estado' IN ('{EC.descripcion}'))

SELECT DISTINCT icodcli 
	FROM exclipro EC
	LEFT JOIN expedien E ON EC.inumexp = E.inumexp AND EC.iyear = E.iyear
	WHERE 
		E.inumexp*CAST(10000 as bigint)+E.iyear IN ({E.inumexp*CAST(10000 as bigint)+E.iyear})
	AND
		E.codsubusu = {E.codsubusu}
	AND
		E.descripcion LIKE '%{E.descripcion}%'
	AND
		E.estado LIKE '%{E.estado}%'
	AND 
		E.dfechaalta BETWEEN '{E.dfechaalta}' AND '{E.dfechaalta}'
	AND
		EC.estadocurso IN ('{EC.estadocurso}')
	AND
	    E.dfechacierre BETWEEN '{E.dfechacierre}' AND '{E.dfechacierre}'
	AND
	    EC.dfechabaja BETWEEN '{EC.dfechabaja}' AND '{EC.dfechabaja}'   
	AND
	    EC.dfmatricula BETWEEN '{EC.dfmatricula}' AND '{EC.dfmatricula}'
	GROUP BY EC.icodcli, EC.inumexp, EC.iyear

	LEFT JOIN clientes C ON EC.icodcli = C.icodcli AND C.tipobd = 0
WHERE 
		C.icodcli IN ({C.icodcli})

	AND 
		C.snombreclicomercial LIKE '%{C.snombreclicomercial}%'

	AND
		C.fechaalta BETWEEN '{C.fechaalta}' AND '{C.fechaalta}'
	AND

	AND 
		EC.estadocurso IN ('{EC.estadocurso}') 
	AND 
		EC.dfechaalta BETWEEN '{EC.dfechaalta}' AND '{EC.dfechaalta}' 
	AND

SELECT DISTINCT EA.inumexp*CAST(10000 as bigint)+EA.iyear as idexp  
FROM expalumnos EA 
LEFT JOIN clientes C ON EA.icodcli = C.icodcli 
LEFT JOIN PrevcobrosExpalumnos PE on PE.inumexpalum = EA.inumexp AND PE.iyearexpalum = EA.iyear 
LEFT JOIN PrevCobros P on P.id = PE.idprevcobros 
LEFT JOIN lineprevcobros L on L.idprevcobros = P.id 
WHERE 
 C.icodcli IN ({C.icodcli}) 
AND 
 C.codsubusu = {C.codsubusu} 
AND 
 C.snombrecli LIKE '%{C.snombrecli}%' 
AND 
 C.estadocli LIKE '%{C.estadocli}%' 
AND 
 C.fechaalta BETWEEN '{C.fechaalta}' AND '{C.fechaalta}' 
AND 
 C.tipofichero LIKE '%{C.tipofichero}%' 
AND 
 EA.estadocurso IN ('{EA.estadocurso}') 
AND 
 EA.dfechaalta BETWEEN '{EA.dfechaalta}' AND '{EA.dfechaalta}' 
AND 
 EA.dfmatricula BETWEEN '{EA.dfmatricula}' AND '{EA.dfmatricula}' 
AND 
 EA.dfechabaja BETWEEN '{EA.dfechabaja}' AND '{EA.dfechabaja}'

SELECT DISTINCT icodcli 
	FROM expalumnos EA
	LEFT JOIN expedien E ON EA.inumexp = E.inumexp AND EA.iyear = E.iyear
	LEFT JOIN PrevcobrosExpalumnos PE ON PE.inumexpalum = EA.inumexp AND PE.iyearexpalum = EA.iyear AND PE.ilineaexpalum = EA.linea 
	LEFT JOIN lineprevcobros LP ON LP.inumexpalum = EA.inumexp AND LP.iyearexpalum = EA.iyear AND LP.ilineaexpalum = EA.linea 
	LEFT JOIN tipoexp TE on E.itipoexp = TE.codigo
	LEFT JOIN centrospredef CE on CE.id = E.idcentros
	WHERE 
		(E.inumexp <> 9999 and E.iyear <> 1899)
	AND
		E.inumexp*CAST(10000 as bigint)+E.iyear IN ({E.inumexp*CAST(10000 as bigint)+E.iyear})
	AND
		E.codsubusu = {E.codsubusu}
	AND
		E.descripcion LIKE '%{E.descripcion}%'
	AND
		E.estado LIKE '%{E.estado}%'
	AND
		EA.estadocurso IN ('{EA.estadocurso}')
	AND 
		E.dfechaalta BETWEEN '{E.dfechaalta}' AND '{E.dfechaalta}'
	AND
		E.dfechacierre BETWEEN '{E.dfechacierre}' AND '{E.dfechacierre}'
	AND
		E.campofechatipo1 BETWEEN '{E.campofechatipo1}' AND '{E.campofechatipo1}'
	AND
		E.campofechatipo2 BETWEEN '{E.campofechatipo2}' AND '{E.campofechatipo2}'
	AND
		EA.dfechabaja BETWEEN '{EA.dfechabaja}' AND '{EA.dfechabaja}'
	AND
		EA.dfmatricula BETWEEN '{EA.dfmatricula}' AND '{EA.dfmatricula}'
	AND
		TE.tipoexp IN ('{TE.tipoexp}')
	AND
		EA.estado1 IN ('{EA.estado1}')	
	AND
		EA.estado2 IN ('{EA.estado2}')
	AND
		EA.estado3 IN ('{EA.estado3}')
	AND
		EA.estado4 IN ('{EA.estado4}')
	AND
		EA.estado5 IN ('{EA.estado5}')
	AND
		EA.estado6 IN ('{EA.estado6}')
	AND
		CE.sdescripcion IN ('{CE.sdescripcion}')
	GROUP BY EA.icodcli, EA.inumexp, EA.iyear
	[campo=HAVING=tienePrevCobros]HAVING (COUNT(PE.idprevcobros) + COUNT(LP.id)) {tienePrevCobros}

SELECT DISTINCT icodopor 
		FROM oporusu 
		LEFT JOIN subusu S ON oporusu.icodsubusu = S.icodsubusu
		LEFT JOIN clientes C ON S.icodsubusu = C.codsubusu AND C.tipobd=1
		WHERE 
			C.icodcli IN ({C.icodcli}) 
			AND
			S.icodsubusu IN ({S.icodsubusu})
			AND
			C.snombrecli LIKE '%{C.snombrecli}%'
			AND 
			C.estadoCli LIKE '%{C.estadoCli}%'
			AND
			C.fechaalta BETWEEN '{C.fechaalta}' AND '{C.fechaalta}'
			AND
			C.tipofichero LIKE '%{C.tipofichero}%'

SELECT DISTINCT TI.idexp FROM ( 
			SELECT I.inumexp*CAST(10000 AS bigint)+I.iyear AS idexp, I.rol AS rol, C.snombrecli AS nombre 
			FROM expIntervinientes I INNER JOIN clientes C ON I.tipo IN (1000, 1001, 1002, 1003, 1004, 1005, 1006, 1007, 1008, 1009, 1010, 1011, 1012, 1013) AND I.codigo = C.icodcli 
			UNION ALL 
			SELECT I.inumexp*CAST(10000 AS bigint)+I.iyear AS idexp, I.rol AS rol, CONT.snombreclicon AS nombre 
			FROM expIntervinientes I INNER JOIN cliecont CONT ON I.tipo = 2000 AND I.codigo = CONT.icodclicon 
			UNION ALL 
			SELECT I.inumexp*CAST(10000 AS bigint)+I.iyear AS idexp, I.rol AS rol, A.snombreabo AS nombre 
			FROM expIntervinientes I INNER JOIN abogados A ON I.tipo IN (2001, 2003) AND I.codigo = A.icodabo 
			UNION ALL 
			SELECT I.inumexp*CAST(10000 AS bigint)+I.iyear AS idexp, I.rol AS rol, P.snombrepro AS nombre 
			FROM expIntervinientes I INNER JOIN procurad P ON I.tipo IN (2002, 2004) AND I.codigo = P.icodpro 
			UNION ALL 
			SELECT I.inumexp*CAST(10000 AS bigint)+I.iyear AS idexp, I.rol AS rol, CO.nombre 
			FROM expIntervinientes I INNER JOIN contacto CO ON I.tipo = 2005 AND I.codigo = CO.codcontacto 
			UNION ALL 
			SELECT I.inumexp*CAST(10000 AS bigint)+I.iyear AS idexp, I.rol AS rol, COL.snombrecol AS nombre 
			FROM expIntervinientes I INNER JOIN colabora COL ON I.tipo = 2006 AND I.codigo = COL.codcolab 
			UNION ALL 
			SELECT I.inumexp*CAST(10000 AS bigint)+I.iyear AS idexp, I.rol AS rol, J.juzgado AS nombre 
			FROM expIntervinientes I INNER JOIN juzgado J ON I.tipo = 2007 AND I.codigo = J.codjuzga 
			UNION ALL 
			SELECT I.inumexp*CAST(10000 AS bigint)+I.iyear AS idexp, I.rol AS rol, O.nombre 
			FROM expIntervinientes I INNER JOIN organism O ON I.tipo = 2008 AND I.codigo = O.codorgan 
			UNION ALL 
			SELECT I.inumexp*CAST(10000 AS bigint)+I.iyear AS idexp, I.rol AS rol, PE.nombre 
			FROM expIntervinientes I INNER JOIN peritos PE ON I.tipo = 2009 AND I.codigo = PE.codigo 
			UNION ALL 
			SELECT I.inumexp*CAST(10000 AS bigint)+I.iyear AS idexp, I.rol AS rol, T.nombre 
			FROM expIntervinientes I INNER JOIN talleres T ON I.tipo = 2010 AND I.codigo = T.codigo 
			UNION ALL 
			SELECT I.inumexp*CAST(10000 AS bigint)+I.iyear AS idexp, I.rol AS rol, P1.Perso1 AS nombre 
			FROM expIntervinientes I INNER JOIN perso1 P1 ON I.tipo = 2011 AND I.codigo = P1.Codigo 
			UNION ALL 
			SELECT I.inumexp*CAST(10000 AS bigint)+I.iyear AS idexp, I.rol AS rol, P2.Perso1 AS nombre 
			FROM expIntervinientes I INNER JOIN perso2 P2 ON I.tipo = 2012 AND I.codigo = P2.Codigo 
			UNION ALL 
			SELECT I.inumexp*CAST(10000 AS bigint)+I.iyear AS idexp, I.rol AS rol, P3.Perso1 AS nombre 
			FROM expIntervinientes I INNER JOIN perso3 P3 ON I.tipo = 2013 AND I.codigo = P3.Codigo 
			UNION ALL 
			SELECT I.inumexp*CAST(10000 AS bigint)+I.iyear AS idexp, I.rol AS rol, P5.Perso1 AS nombre 
			FROM expIntervinientes I INNER JOIN perso5 P5 ON I.tipo = 2014 AND I.codigo = P5.Codigo 
			UNION ALL 
			SELECT I.inumexp*CAST(10000 AS bigint)+I.iyear AS idexp, I.rol AS rol, P4.Perso1 AS nombre 
			FROM expIntervinientes I INNER JOIN perso4 P4 ON I.tipo = 2015 AND I.codigo = P4.Codigo 
			UNION ALL 
			SELECT I.inumexp*CAST(10000 AS bigint)+I.iyear AS idexp, I.rol AS rol, COLI.snombrecol AS nombre 
			FROM expIntervinientes I INNER JOIN colitiga COLI ON I.tipo = 2016 AND I.codigo = COLI.codcolit 
		) TI 
		WHERE 
		TI.rol LIKE ('%{TI.rol}%') 
		AND 
		TI.nombre LIKE '%{TI.nombre}%'

SELECT DISTINCT PC.id 
	FROM expedien E
	LEFT JOIN expalumnos EA on EA.inumexp = E.inumexp AND EA.iyear = E.iyear
	LEFT JOIN tipoexp TE on E.itipoexp = TE.codigo
	INNER JOIN prevcobros PC ON PC.icodclirelacionado = EA.icodcli
	WHERE 
		(E.inumexp <> 9999 and E.iyear <> 1899)
	AND
		E.inumexp*CAST(10000 as bigint)+E.iyear IN ({E.inumexp*CAST(10000 as bigint)+E.iyear})
	AND
		E.codsubusu = {E.codsubusu}
	AND
		E.descripcion LIKE '%{E.descripcion}%'
	AND
		E.estado LIKE '%{E.estado}%'
	AND
		EA.estadocurso IN ('{EA.estadocurso}')
	AND 
		E.dfechaalta BETWEEN '{E.dfechaalta}' AND '{E.dfechaalta}'
	AND
		E.dfechacierre BETWEEN '{E.dfechacierre}' AND '{E.dfechacierre}'
	AND
		TE.tipoexp IN ('{TE.tipoexp}')	
    AND
		E.campofechatipo1 BETWEEN '{E.campofechatipo1}' AND '{E.campofechatipo1}'
	AND
		E.campofechatipo2 BETWEEN '{E.campofechatipo2}' AND '{E.campofechatipo2}'
	GROUP BY PC.id, EA.inumexp, EA.iyear

SELECT DISTINCT o.icodopor
	FROM oporcli o
	LEFT JOIN clientes c ON c.icodcli = o.icodcli
	LEFT JOIN oporcli tar on tar.icodcli = c.icodcli
	WHERE 
	    tar.tipooportunidad = 1
	AND
		tar.oportunidad LIKE '%{tar.oportunidad}%'
	AND
		tar.icodusu = {tar.icodusu} 
	AND 
		tar.dfecha BETWEEN '{tar.dfecha}' AND '{tar.dfecha}'
	AND
		tar.fechacierre BETWEEN '{tar.fechacierre}' AND '{tar.fechacierre}'
	AND
		tar.fechaseguimiento BETWEEN '{tar.fechaseguimiento}' AND '{tar.fechaseguimiento}'
	AND
		tar.estado IN ('{tar.estado}')
	AND
		tar.etapa IN ('{tar.etapa}')
	AND
		tar.fuente IN ('{tar.fuente}')
	AND
		tar.tipo IN ('{tar.tipo}')
	AND 
		o.icodopor IS NOT NULL
NOT EXISTS(SELECT TOP 1 id FROM [[instancia]advAboUsu[empresa]].[dbo].segcli S WHERE S.icodcli = [nomTablaGestor].icodcli AND S.esTratamiento = 2)
